    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Install Glow Plug</title>
        <figure id="f1200471" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figeg2/EG2671.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="yes"/>
            <caption>Installing the Glow Plugs</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Glow Plug</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Torque Wrench</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <para>Apply Never-Seez&#174; to the threads of the glow plugs. Install the glow plugs into the cylinder head.
            Tighten the glow plugs to the special torque value.
        </para>
